skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to weekly updates from LowVisionTech.com about topics related to Vision loss due to Macular Degeneration, Glaucoma, Diabetes and other eye diseases, and vision rehabilitation . You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
